headline: Decentralized Finance is Going to 'Explode': Kraken's Santori
summary: Kraken Senior Advisor Marco Santori says "you have to think about stablecoins as one of those critical bits of technology that will allow other things to be built upon it." He tells Sonali Basak and Tim Stenovec he believes decentralized finance is going to "explode" once there is more stabilized use of stablecoins.

headline: Should You Buy Serve Robotics Stock After Its 65% Plunge? Nvidia's Recent Move Might Hold the Answer.
summary: Serve Robotics (NASDAQ: SERV) develops autonomous robots that have already completed thousands of food deliveries on behalf of platforms like Uber's Uber Eats.  In fact, the company has a contract with Uber to deploy thousands of new robots by the end of 2025, which will pave the way for an expansion into new geographic markets.  Serve's robots are powered by Nvidia's (NASDAQ: NVDA) Jetson Orin platform, which provides the hardware and software required to run advanced robotics and computer vision.
